data.description: Welcome to 800 Harrisburg Ln! This well maintained home is situated on an exceptionally spacious lot in the heart of a highly sought-after neighborhood in Mount Juliet, with top rated schools! The grand foyer welcomes you with soaring ceilings, and an open-concept design seamlessly connects the gourmet kitchen, featuring high-end appliances and an island made for serious cooks and gracious hosts! Master suite separated on the primary level, also a HUGE bonus room upstairs. Outside, the sprawling backyard oasis beckons, boasting lush landscaping, a huge covered deck, and plenty of room for outdoor entertainment. Roof is only 2 years old! Convenient to Nashville, Providence Shopping, Highway 40, and Lebanon. Preferred lender incentive of 1% of loan value towards rate buy down and/or closing costs for qualified buyers! Seller to provide paint allowance.
